{"tid":486904,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"九份十分一日遊行程點plan好","createTime":"2017-12-02T09:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T07:22:07.000Z","uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2a98017b2f6eaa50d4aff8e61854222b2034d97b","tid":486904,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"上網搵過資料<br />\n應該係台北車站搭火車去瑞芳 之後可以搭巴士去九份<br />\n十分青桐果就可以搭平溪線<br />\n但係我諗住去左十分青桐果d先 之後先去九份睇夜景<br />\n咁係瑞芳可以點去十分？<br />\n之後玩完平溪線可以點樣去返九份同返瑞芳？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b887a8cc5f6984a84bd46ec20422b35d2c596bb2","tid":486904,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:06:16.000Z","msg":"返瑞芳轉巴士"},{"pid":"5b59ae79b804c87158187a1b4012da9188745218","tid":486904,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"包車啦"},{"pid":"b2f4420c14b97d67e53fd3eded3c4898589d228d","tid":486904,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>包車啦</blockquote><br />\nBtw十分有的士可以坐去九份<br />\n好似唔係好貴"},{"pid":"e89929ca644ce305aeb2648704b764fa6d08af40","tid":486904,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返瑞芳轉巴士</blockquote><br />\n即係都可以搭巴士去平溪線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672b6d1375de41b7a2ebee8242fce924c854d3f7","tid":486904,"uid":16469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T17:41:02.000Z","msg":"九份十分 去唔去埋菁桐好？<br />\n應該預幾點岀發？想買十分瀑布<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a81e7b99640929e2ff2ba196c78c5bf8dd99259","tid":486904,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T18:56:19.000Z","msg":"朝早出發啦"},{"pid":"3e609b91f36fee24d6dc1623a55fdcb517b3b1b0","tid":486904,"uid":13514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"瑞芳搭平溪線列車去十分<br />\n再搭返平溪線列車去瑞芳<br />\n係瑞芳再搭巴士去九份"},{"pid":"187dee8300c1c946355a6ff2d5c9e2bd604cb811","tid":486904,"uid":16469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"青茼車站 值唔值得去？"},{"pid":"29c18bdc5b38810f75e08b3a1ee5ce23c865d8e0","tid":486904,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T20:12:28.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"be364398a847d787b8f38b3c78211afad989f8ae","tid":486904,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T20:15:22.000Z","msg":"如果唔一大早出發既話就放棄菁桐"},{"pid":"412df2fc645cb10677ed57ff9a8c3a3a9db66cbc","tid":486904,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T20:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔一大早出發既話就放棄菁桐</blockquote><br />\n俾我揀就去菁桐唔去九份<br />\n不過，各人喜好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b105ead07b5690bb756eee7a2c9d34d7a7e75695","tid":486904,"uid":87471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T21:13:21.000Z","msg":"其實時間充裕既話真係唔建議十分九分一齊..<br />\n十分d車好疏，你要預時間會好麻煩<br />\n你仲想去埋菁桐會有d趕<br />\n同埋九分大約7點到好多舖頭都會關門<br />\n你咁夜上去靜係睇景又唔係好值"},{"pid":"4449aeb3e703f9a02d1afc7089d6ac61a3e5c6cd","tid":486904,"uid":10123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"菁桐去過一次，唔係要影相打卡可以唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一次試過淨係去十分-&gt;九份-&gt;廟口夜市<br />\n睇定台鐵班次一日去得哂"},{"pid":"9b9b14b1d01cf4df091a553eee15fab67674d1c3","tid":486904,"uid":51748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T21:57:20.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ea0c37520ebdeb2f69f235a8069eee26f70c9221","tid":486904,"uid":16469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T06:45:07.000Z","msg":"九份十分個日 去基隆夜市好定寧夏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留得3晚 一晚去饒河 一晚去樹林興仁"},{"pid":"a77a2b5a9c9ecb8b7d30221537c49ec93eb885c4","tid":486904,"uid":1903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T06:47:42.000Z","msg":"包車啦<br />\n坐死人火車好麻煩<br />\n又迫"},{"pid":"1621ffe7293c103120c3de3ff7e2d0d5a5efb9d2","tid":486904,"uid":102358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"九份夜晚去乜都無架<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n景又無人地吹得咁靚<br />\n舖頭都全部關晒門<br />\n建議日頭去<br />\n<br />\n之前試過去忠孝復興站諗住搭公車入九份<br />\n其實坐公車係坐勁耐先入到<br />\n一出地鐵站又有啲的士佬係到r入拼車<br />\n價錢係合理既 但實際唔記得<br />\n拼車姐係如果你兩個人坐<br />\n佢會再r多4個人一齊坐入九份 視乎佢架車大小<br />\n我果陣係同4個日本人一齊坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大約個幾鐘就入到去<br />\n<br />\n去完九份就坐公車出返瑞芳車站<br />\n再係瑞芳搭去十分<br />\n十分會有車直接返瑞芳<br />\n唔洗再返九份去瑞芳咁麻煩<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686de46b4ad0594112189c045fba3400d2ac48a3","tid":486904,"uid":102358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九份夜晚去乜都無架<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n景又無人地吹得咁靚<br />\n舖頭都全部關晒門<br />\n建議日頭去<br />\n<br />\n之前試過去忠孝復興站諗住搭公車入九份<br />\n其實坐公車係坐勁耐先入到<br />\n一出地鐵站又有啲的士佬係到r<span style=\"color: red;\">人</span>拼車<br />\n價錢係合理既 但實際唔記得<br />\n拼車姐係如果你兩個人坐<br />\n佢會再r多4個人一齊坐入九份 視乎佢架車大小<br />\n我果陣係同4個日本人一齊坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大約個幾鐘就入到去<br />\n<br />\n去完九份就坐公車出返瑞芳車站<br />\n再係瑞芳搭去十分<br />\n十分會有車直接返瑞芳<br />\n唔洗再返九份去瑞芳咁麻煩<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}